====Usage notes====
The [[w:Kangxi dictionary|Kangxi dictionary]] considers {{lang|mul|真}} as an [[unorthodox]] form ({{zh-l|俗字*}}) of {{l|mul|眞}}. However, the traditional Kangxi form {{l|mul|眞}} with {{l|mul|匕}} on top is rarely used nowadays. In modern times, {{lang|mul|真}} is considered the orthodox form in all regions except South Korea.

